net.hudup.core.data

Class RatingTriple

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.hudup.core.data.RatingTriple
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, TextParsable

    public class RatingTriple
extends java.lang.Object
implements Cloneable, TextParsable, java.io.Serializable
    This class contains the rating that a user gives on an item, including three following parts:
    • The rating represented by Rating class.
    • User identification (user ID).
    • Item identification (item ID).
    Version:
    10.0
    Author:
    Loc Nguyen
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
